@@TJvScrollingLabel.NoGrap
Summary
  Indicates whether the text scrolls over the full width of the label.
Description
  Set NoGrap to True to scroll the text over the width of the scroll text only. Set NoGrap to False 
  to scroll the text over the full width of the label.
