@@TJvScrollingLabel.OnCtl3DChanged
Summary
  Occurs when the Ctl3D property of the label changes.
Description
  Write an OnCtl3DChanged event handler to take specific action when the Ctl3D property changes.
See Also
  OnParentColorChange
